        "content": "<p>uweigand submitted <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12707#pullrequestreview-4015354187\">PR review</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The general approach looks good, but see a few issues inline.</p>\n<p>Also, you should add encoding tests for the new instructions to <code>inst/emit_tests.rs</code>.</p>\n</blockquote>",
